        "meta_description": "50 Years in the making. The mysteries of a building, the New York World's Fair Pavilion by Philip Johnson, is the subject of Kickstarter project MODERN RUIN: A World's Fair Pavilion, Matthew Silva's new film about the abandoned 20th-century icon.",
